{"tid":1441974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日做左一日和理飛，有感而發","createTime":"2019-08-10T19:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:59:19.000Z","uid":98520,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"88b7172273cd82e72a02a5343a5d861ce26f06ba","tid":1441974,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:24:35.000Z","msg":"今日一到機場，見到有班手足手持標語周圍遊走，有d就企係到向路過人士派發傳單，真係辛苦哂你地。<br />\n不過係接機果到，我覺得有d地方要改善。叫口號麻煩大家唔好再成日叫香港人加油，依d完全係用黎自己打飛機，外國人根本唔明做緊乜，反而叫多d <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">stand with Hong Kong,fight for freedom</span></span> 仲好。麻煩大家做和理非唔緊要，但希望大家可以專注返我地既目的，文宣要做返好d。出面成班手足周圍跑緊打遊擊，佢地無冷氣涼嫁，我地有冷氣涼，但竟然經常叫香港人加油，依d圍爐口號，對唔對得住出面班手足，對唔對得住被捕義士。我預左會有人話我，但我真係睇唔過眼，有感而發，希望大家可以反思一下。<br />\n<br />\n最近都唔見哂關於遊行、戰術既post ，等我都幫手宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDR75Cg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDR75Cg.jpg&h=68fb7a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaXrBJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaXrBJW.jpg&h=cf983a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqS7maC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqS7maC.png&h=38da018b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2LA8P3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2LA8P3X.jpg&h=2935df7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFyZchh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFyZchh.jpg&h=6f08d875&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkcnUvD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkcnUvD.jpg&h=535c5d63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijzJDXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijzJDXi.png&h=55e1a70d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b294a352788caa044f4ad04535ee577783198a2b","tid":1441974,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":